    "body": "### Contact Details (e.g. Tox ID or email)\n\n_No response_\n\n### qTox Version\n\nv1.18.2\n\n### Commit Hash\n\n_No response_\n\n### Toxcore Version\n\n_No response_\n\n### Qt Version\n\n_No response_\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\n1. Start qTox with Flatpak\n2. Login to your account\n3. Close qTox window\n4. start qTox with Flatpak again and try to login the same profile. It will say \"the profile is already in use\"\n5. `ps aux | grep -i qtox` - You'll see that qTox doesn't close when closing the UI. \n\n\n\n\n### Observed Behavior\n\nqTox from Flatpak keeps running in the background after closing the window\n\n### Expected Behavior\n\nThe whole application should close when closing the window\n\n### Reproducibility\n\nAlways\n\n### Operating System\n\nLinux\n\n### Operating System version/distro/name/etc.\n\nArch linux\n\n### Relevant log output\n\n```shell\n\n```",
